   *
   * ## Example
   *
   * ```javascript
   * // create a DataSet
   * const data = new vis.DataSet()
   *
   * // add items
   * const ids = data.add([
   *   { id: 1, text: 'item 1' },
   *   { id: 2, text: 'item 2' },
   *   { text: 'item without an id' }
   * ])
